message.body: How was your 4th?? Was Wuthering heights good?
It was so dark and sad and I think had necrophilia but I am not sure! Great night. HUNTER went off the wagon and is in bed moaning for biscuits.
Haha you better make him some biscuits! Downtown was good! We went to China town and got dinner and then walked to Franklin square park and played mini g
olf and rode the carousel...it was such a nice night!
That sounds fun! The weather was great!
We gonna go to penns landing tonight to watch fireworks from Camden if you're interested! :)
Let me know when you guys go! Gotta take care of this meat pile so he don't puke on my sheets.
